  "instruction": "Write an HTML5 blockquote citing a customer review. Include a cite element referencing the reviewer name.",
  "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n    <title>Customer quote</title>\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <blockquote cite=\"https://example.com/reviews/42\">\n      <p>The onboarding checklist saved our team hours every week.</p>\n      <footer>— <cite>Jordan Lee</cite>, Operations lead</footer>\n    </blockquote>\n  </body>\n</html>",
